     of the central variables.  The second key 'dpairInds' also contains 3 lists
     of the corresponding indices to 'dpairVars'.",
     EXAMPLE lines ///
	     W = QQ[x,y,Dx,Dy, WeylAlgebra => {x=>Dx,y=>Dy}]
